features: 【P-ARGB Fan Temperature Control Controller】:Direct SATA Power Input, support 8 PWM intelligent temperature control (4-pin) + 10 5V ARGB interface (3-pin) + remote wireless remote control three in one function, Enables users to optimally expand cooling capability within the chassis
【Cool Luminous Shell】: The fan thermostat looks like a sports car, length: 118mm, width: 55mm, height: 24mm
【Product Accessories】: The package contains RGB fan thermostat x1, SATA power cable x1, temperature control cable x1, motherboard sync cable x1

【Wireless Remote Control Function】: The controller is equipped with a wireless remote control switch, which can freely switch between the hosting mode and the remote control mode. There are about 365 light modes to choose from
【PWM Fan Controller】: The back uses a magnet device, which is easy to be attached to the inside of the chassis for easy installation. Supports 5v motherboards such as ASUS, MSI, Gigabyte, and ASRock.
body.description: The new P-ARGB temperature control controller has a new cool luminous shell. The remote control mode supports up to 360 multiple modes, including static lighting, breathing mode, flashing mode, rainbow mode, colorful loop, comet effect, lightning effect, wave effect, music rhythm and more! Product accessories includes: Fan controller*1; Remote control*1; SATA power cord *1; Temperature control line *1; Motherboard sync line *1; Computer fan HUB temperature control fan integrator，Support 8 PWM (4 PIN interface) intelligent temperature control, 10 ARGB fans (3pin) ,Support up to 18 fans Front interface: 4 PWM interfaces, the first one in red is recommended as a CPU fan interface; 4 ARGB interfaces Rear interface: 4 PWM interfaces, 4 ARGB interfaces Left interface: the two-pin interface is the restart switch interface (restart button can not be connected), the middle red 4pin is the sata power supply interface, and the third interface is the 5V 3pin motherboard interface Right interface: 2 ARGB interfaces (can be connected to the computer light belt), the two-pin interface is the temperature control signal interface You can freely use your imagination and find more surprises. Note: Please be sure to install when the power is off, and don’t insert any wrong interface, so as not to cause a short circuit to burn your equipment
